# server/ (Express + tRPC)

- Keep API logic inside tRPC routers and core services under `server/_core/`.
- Use Drizzle helpers from `server/db.ts` instead of ad-hoc SQL where possible.
- After backend changes, run `npm run test` and, if needed, `npm run db:push` for schema updates.
